    "Other parameters are involved in the fermion rotation from flavour to mass eigenstates.",
    "We denote by V ψ L(R) the matrix rotating left (right)-handed components of the vector of fermions (ψ 1L(R), ψ 2 L(R), ψ 3 L(R)) with the same quantum numbers in the three generations, to obtain a diagonal mass matrix ( Mψ) D:( Mψ) D = ( V ψ L) † Mψ V ψ R.(17)In terms of the rotated fields, Eq.",
